article_title: UnitedHealth Group CEO Expects To Overcome ObamaCare Challenges

article_metadata.description: Though there will be costly pressures to insurers for providing coverage to uninsured Americans signing up for health benefits under the Affordable Care Act, the nation’s largest health insurer, UnitedHealth Group (UNH), expects growth from new business under the law.
